environment.city

Class EnvVar

  • java.lang.Object
    • environment.city.EnvVar

  • public class EnvVar
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores every global variables of the simulation. Due to Repast Simphony management of objects during simulation it is required to have a pool of available objects that are cleaned between simulations.
    Author:
    Simon Pageaud
